{"tid":2192983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"低智藍絲投訴廉署出醜！辦事處「榮光」盆裁取材日本卡通片","createTime":"2020-09-07T13:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T18:04:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ea46bb293cb6a53be68403f10200938d7c522bad","tid":2192983,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"藍絲頻頻出動做紅衞兵，各大機構人心惶惶，皆因佢哋「有殺錯、冇放過」，不時傷及無辜，但當然亦凸顯佢哋有幾咁高嘅水平。<br />\n<br />\n最近中彈嘅係廉政公署，話說藍絲群組近日瘋傳，廉署九龍灣分部公然支持「港獨」，鐵證如山。到底係咩鐵證？原來佢哋辦事處分部放咗棵小盆裁，而個花盆上竟然有「榮光」字眼，不容抵賴，據聞唔少藍絲已經去信廉署投訴，做好國家嘅好兒女！<br />\n<br />\n八方睇過藍絲疫傳張相，個小小花盆的確印有「榮光」二字，但細心一睇，其實仲有兩隻字見唔到，完整係有四隻字：「敗者榮光」。咦，之咪就係Wing Gundam系列故事劇名《敗者榮光》？當然藍絲作風梗係，有理無理投訴咗先.......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/B3W74LE52JGXDFWZLA65OZOZJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FB3W74LE52JGXDFWZLA65OZOZJM%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=e06e5844\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FB3W74LE52JGXDFWZLA65OZOZJM%2F&h=0c1e293b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/B3W74LE52JGXDFWZLA65OZOZJM/</a>"},{"pid":"3401f802020e3ad93d6495eb085e110fd255f55f","tid":2192983,"uid":274532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T13:06:56.000Z","msg":"廉政公署支持港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab58906b07dadc578f4da52b58589b32c61a7215","tid":2192983,"uid":321059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T13:08:04.000Z","msg":"真係人一藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8e86c221f405ddd99183471a487cacfc27413f","tid":2192983,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ERkAxy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ERkAxy.jpg&h=11ae2a1